{"tid":1429534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「攻擊性武器」 木棍 vs 觀星筆 （反擊警方理論）","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:36:28.000Z","uid":103353,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"02af42deeffdfb8bb228ffbfd126d08272d9a960","tid":1429534,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"最重要係比較返21/7 元朗警方稱現場無攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n正常人都會認為木棍、鐵枝攻擊性比雷射筆大<br />\n點解當時冇即刻拘捕？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔使舉旗開槍驅散人群？<br />\n<br />\n答案有3個<br />\n1. 元朗係警黑合作<br />\n2. 觀星筆係濫捕、白色恐佈<br />\n3. 以上偕是<br />\n<br />\n帶出<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">執法不公</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嚴重損害香港法治</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講多少少攻擊性<br />\n<br />\n除左考慮會否造成傷害（牙簽都可以傷到視網膜ga)<br />\n要考慮埋可能性<br />\n<br />\n向2米內<br />\n你認為木棍，鐵枝傷到你機會大<br />\n定枝觀星筆射中你隻眼10秒機會大？"},{"pid":"c0dc7e1af95cfba04d6f77317006aeff9fade0ce","tid":1429534,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"木棍射唔到紙出煙"},{"pid":"2863aa383b68ed3e47e59dc33a359601376943eb","tid":1429534,"uid":103353,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c0dc7e1af95cfba04d6f77317006aeff9fade0ce","tid":1429534,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"木棍射唔到紙出煙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"我拎木棍<br />\n警拎觀星筆<br />\n<br />\n試下邊個打贏"},{"pid":"b3675210a3309272b040841f7b213e48e7cf9d32","tid":1429534,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2863aa383b68ed3e47e59dc33a359601376943eb","tid":1429534,"uid":103353,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c0dc7e1af95cfba04d6f77317006aeff9fade0ce","tid":1429534,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"木棍射唔到紙出煙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"我拎木棍<br />\n警拎觀星筆<br />\n<br />\n試下邊個打贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht